<B><FONT SIZE=+1>APPLICATION SCENARIOS</FONT></B><B></B>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>1. Video-On-Demand (<a href="c10afig/f10-2.JPG">fig. 10-2</a>)
</FONT>
<UL>
<LI>
<FONT SIZE=+1>The client accesses multimedia data such as entertainment
programs, news and travel information, using a set-top box connected
to his TV set and a remote control for control commands</FONT></LI>
</UL>
<FONT SIZE=+1>2. World-Wide-Web</FONT>
<UL>
<LI>
<FONT SIZE=+1>Millions of interconnected computers act as information
servers and/or clients</FONT></LI>

<LI>
<FONT SIZE=+1>The clients access multimedia information in the form of
text, images, audio and video from various web servers</FONT></LI>
</UL>
